    - target: {fileID: 5094079699547920132, guid: 9bfd7f27d8469084a8127772853935bb, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Takahiro made this sculpture from the Reduction series in 2014. He
        made it from local clay and fired it outdoors at Tenkawa Benzaiten Shrine,
        in the area of Yoshino, in Nara Prefecture, Japan. Ash collected on the figure\u2019s
        head and shoulders, creating a glistening glaze that drips down his face
        and chest."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
